review_title: Planetary group is a scam contacted the…
review_content: Planetary group is a scam contacted the real planetary group via email and there was no shadow of a doubt that planetarygroupuk.com is not associated with the company and they are trying to get them shut down...the review below is fake I mean look at the picture
I found this platform legit. There is no long-term investment. I can withdraw my commission daily. However, it's a little bit expensive, but the return is awesome. I'm happy.

Although the supervisor is generally patient and helpful it just seems to be an elaborate scam .   It’s cleverly constructed so you think it’s easy money .  Firstly the processes to supposedly recieve your money is complex and needed to download two apps ,  some contradictions also .  But money never recieved in fact they ask you to deposit money to complete process up to 150 pounds at least .   The actual work to claim money is simple but odd as you just give 5 stars to music items .    First clue .   A lot of wasted time .

Ok, I decided to give this service a fair shot because I had read more reviews than bad, but after using it and comparing it to ther services I see clearly that they are too expensive for the service. Also, I recognize that there is no guaranteed numbers but the results were significantly less than I expected. Avoid this, don't waste your money as I did, be smarter than me.
